room_title: Escape room "The Race" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
room_description:
It’s the final race of the season for the Vintage Race League and you and your main competitor are neck and neck in the points race. Your crew just received a call from the mechanic that both you and the other team’s racecars were sabotaged last night.
The car presentation deadline will give you only 60 minutes to find the spare carburetor at the Race and Restoration Shop. Good luck getting the security code to the Parts Department and getting the replacement four-barrel carburetor back to your team. Only one team can be successful!
There are two identical rooms available at the location, each for 2-8 players.
